ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Tourism of BRENDA HOLDER of Clearwater County, Alberta, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission, to hold office during pleasure for a term of four years, in the place of Patricia (Pat) Macdonald, whose term has expired.
